    {"hook": "Your smartphone can replace a professional scanner.", "content": "Adobe Scan or Microsoft Lens turns your phone camera into a high-quality scanner. It auto-detects edges, removes shadows, and enhances text. Export as PDF or JPEG instantly.", "category": "phone", "tool": "Adobe Scan"},
