    {"hook": "Compare flight prices across every airline at once.", "content": "Use Google Flights or Skyscanner. Enter your destination and dates. It searches hundreds of airlines and shows the cheapest options. Set a price alert and get notified when fares drop.", "category": "productivity", "tool": "Google Flights"},
