    {"hook": "Track your spending without any manual effort.", "content": "Use a budgeting app like YNAB or EveryDollar. Connect your bank accounts and credit cards. Transactions are automatically categorized. See exactly where your money goes without entering anything.", "category": "productivity", "tool": "YNAB"},
